                    <h1>Las clasificaciones de las Estad&iacute;sticas de Seguros para M&eacute;xico</h1>
                        <p><a href="http://www.bbb.org/central-northern-western-arizona/business-reviews/insurance-companies/mexico-insurance-professionals-in-flagstaff-az-83004848" title="BBB Reliability Seal"><span itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject"><img src="{{ site.url }}{{site.baseurl}}/images/Reliability-Seal.png" alt="BBB Reliability Seal" class="img-rt img-responsive" width="50" height="76" itemprop="contentURL"></span></a><strong>&iquest;Es su compa&ntilde;a de seguros de M&eacute;xico acredita?</strong></p>
                        <p><em>Read past years findings on how Mexican Tourist Auto companies performed.</em></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><p><strong><a href="{{ site.url }}{{site.baseurl}}/pdf/AMIS-2016-Tourist-Auto-Mexpro-May-2017.pdf" title="Resultados de Auto Turista Mexico 2016">Resultados de Auto Turista Mexico 2016</a></strong></p></li>
                            <li><p><strong><a href="{{ site.url }}{{site.baseurl}}/pdf/AMIS-2015-Results-Mexpro.pdf" title="Resultados de Auto Turista Mexico 2015">Resultados de Auto Turista Mexico 2015</a></strong></p></li>
                            <li><p><strong><a href="{{ site.url }}{{site.baseurl}}/pdf/AMIS-2013-Results-Spanish.pdf" title="Resultados de Auto Turista Mexico 2013">Resultados de Auto Turista Mexico 2013</a></strong></p></li>
                            <li><p><strong><a href="{{ site.url }}{{site.baseurl}}/pdf/AMIS2012-mx.pdf" title="Resultados Auto Turista Mexico 2012">Resultados de Auto Turista Mexico 2012</a></strong></p></li>
